[ISBN Bingo](http://www.twitter.com/gyldendal) Minimalist gamification (or is it just a game?) by Danish publishing company Gyldendal. Each Friday the crane (corresponding to their logo) draws 2 numbers and tweets them using the #fredagsbog (Friday Book - a customer engagement activity that asks people what they are reading on Fridays). The participants then need to find a book with an ISBN number with the drawn numbers as the last 2 digits. The first person to tweet ”BANKO + the author of the book + title + #fredagsbog + #ISBNBingo” wins (You have to remember the plus signs). The Winner receives a current book or one just to be released by the publisher. A very simple game, but also very effective. Full rules here: http://gyldendal.dk/artikler/isbnbingofall11 <br>
